member.remarks:
if the containers contain the following blob items ("mycontainer/foo/a", "mycontainer/foo/b/c", "mycontainer/foo/b/d", "mycontainer/bar"), 
            then listing blobs under "mycontainer/foo/" will result in {blob "mycontainer/foo/a", blobdirectory "mycontainer/foo/b/"} if this flag is set to false and 
            
            and {"mycontainer/foo/a", "mycontainer/foo/b/c", "mycontainer/foo/b/d"} if the flag is set to true.
